title: (Thurs Full) Why Was Amy Having a Bad Morning Today? + Top 15 Most Played Songs at Radio Game + Bobby Gives Away A Copy of Kid’s Book If You Can Spot The Lie
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) Why Was Amy Having a Bad Morning Today? + Top 15 Most Played Songs at Radio Game + Bobby Gives Away A Copy of Kid’s Book If You Can Spot The Lie
description:
Eddie said he saw Amy in a frantic state this morning and wonders what is going on in her life. Bobby has a list of the Top 15 most played songs at radio of all-time. The members of the show try to identify them to win a prize for a caller.
